title: Episode 346: Mile High Club (Feat. Shenseea)
itunes:title: Episode 346: Mile High Club (Feat. Shenseea)
description:
Superstar, Shenseea joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest album 'Alpha.' The ladies discuss some of Shenseea's newest hits, such as 'Lick' and 'The Sidechick Song.' During this convo, Shenseea opens up about her son knowing all the words to 'Lick,' as well as her stance on once being a side-chick. Shenseea opens up about her favorite position, what she wants to try (sexually) in the future, and she even admits to masturbating on the plane! Enjoy!
